g":"違犯國安法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:46:26.000Z","msg":"樓主請 pin <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb864e4a1a43678283af5b054ceb74423e4c5da","tid":2153854,"uid":122513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c43be0210d5bce57c2389c2cd50a7dda883a441","tid":2153854,"uid":363977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T19:53:37.000Z","msg":"或者係意外都得 總之唔會俾人發現係自殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:23:28.000Z","msg":"&quot;力益多&quot;，看來你心中盛載著的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀。人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，到我們的網站   <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7UngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=57344314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>    。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（      <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7UngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=1b6706a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php</a>     ）。 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"585cbdaba883d5214708924fe8915af9fd814c85","tid":2153854,"uid":65638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:27:39.000Z","msg":"我教你，老死應該唔會俾人發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d637dc564fcfb9c09a88ba048f4b4d6969202c","tid":2153854,"uid":52406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited